title: Most Authors of Major Superconductor Claim Seek Retraction
description: Eight of the 11 authors are asking to retract a paper on a room-temperature superconductor, but Ranga Dias, the physicist who led the research, continued to defend the findings.

title: A Founder of the Crypto Hedge Fund Three Arrows Capital Is Arrested
description: Su Zhu, a founder of Three Arrows Capital, a cryptocurrency hedge fund that collapsed last year, was arrested in Singapore.

title: Supreme Court to Hear Challenges to State Laws on Social Media
description: The tech industry argues that laws in Florida and Texas, prompted by conservative complaints about censorship by tech platforms, violate the First Amendment.

title: Fact Checkers Take Stock of Their Efforts: ‘It’s Not Getting Better’
description: The momentum behind organizations that aim to combat online falsehoods has started to taper off.
